    <title>[转]Android中黄色警告提示强迫症</title>
    <link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2013/07/30/%E8%BD%ACandroid%E4%B8%AD%E9%BB%84%E8%89%B2%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E5%BC%BA%E8%BF%AB%E7%97%87/</link>
